								  The World's Leading Supplier of Custom Golf Vacations  

								



								For 27 spectacular years, SGH Golf has been arranging Golf tours to the World's finest golf destinations and tournaments.  We offer Scotland Golf Vacation Tours, Masters Golf Tournament Tickets and Hospitality, Ireland Golf Vacation Tours, British Open Golf Tickets, Ryder Cup Ticket Packages, Pebble Beach Golf Packages and Custom Golf Packages to England, Spain, Portugal, Mexico, The US Open and President's Cup.  Please look through our website, as we are confident you will find a golf vacation destination to fulfill your dreams. 

								SGH Golf will customize your vacation, sales meeting, or incentive trip to meet your specific needs.  Whether you are planning to travel alone, with a few friends, or in a large group, SGH Golf will arrange your vacation and give you the special attention to detail you deserve.  This individual attention has continually attracted people to SGH Golf for over 27 years and keeps them coming back! 

								         

