								WHY CHOOSE SGH GOLF? 

								Why choose SGH Golf?  Our courteous staff has many years of experience in the golf travel industry and it is our pleasure to assist you with your golf vacation plans.  We take pride in our work as it provides our clients with memories to last a lifetime.  We realize that you, the customer, are our most important asset.  100% customer satisfaction is our goal.  Give us a call when you are ready to start planning and the rest is easy! 

								Please take a moment to look at some of our sample itineraries; they are just small examples of what we can provide.  All of our trips can be customized to your exact needs and budget. 

								We encourage you to experience all that this great game can offer, be it teeing off at St. Andrews Old Course or watching the final match at the Ryder Cup.  Take it from us; a one week golf vacation package will make for a lifetime of memories!! 

